{"title":"戴口罩的春天","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴口罩的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴口罩的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们辜负了绿水青山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的野花自开自落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婉转的鸟语说给流泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从国家主席到读书少年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在还击着非典的挑战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能串亲访友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们用电话问安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个学校封闭式读书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个乡村封闭式种田……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活被切成一块块蛋糕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷落了酒楼歌馆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在家里，消毒，熏香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要出门，量体温，受检……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个人都在祈祷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早一天结束灾难……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天是不该戴口罩的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天是风香雨甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天是山水的邀请，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天是花草的呼唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了春天不再戴口罩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要吸取教训，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总结经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要深谋远虑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万别目光短浅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对那乱吃野生的酒宴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对那乱养宠物的危险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对环境的恶化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对空气的污染。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们思索：怎样善待自然？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们思索：怎样建设家园？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要未雨绸缪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防患于未然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不可临渴掘井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨来买伞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去迎接春天不再戴口罩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去踏青，去聚会，去狂欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去绿水青山中徜徉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去和小花小草交谈……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}